'''2015年義大利大獎賽'''（{{lang-en|2015 Italian Grand Prix}}），官方名稱為'''2015年一級方程式賽車義大利大獎賽'''（{{lang-it|Formula 1 Gran Premio d'Italia 2015}}）<ref name="formal"/>，是2015年9月6日舉辦於[[義大利|義大利]]的一場[[一級方程式賽車|一級方程式賽車]]賽事。比賽在[[國立蒙札賽車場|國立蒙札賽車場]]進行，總計53圈。這是[[2015年世界一級方程式錦標賽|2015年世界一級方程式錦標賽]]的第12場分站賽事。<ref name="15 calendar">{{cite news |title=World Motor Sport Council 2014 – Beijing |work=FIA.com |publisher=[[Fédération_Internationale_de_l'Automobile|Fédération Internationale de l'Automobile]] |url=http://www.fia.com/news/world-motor-sport-council-2014-beijing |date=2014-09-12 |accessdate=2015-03-01 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150807133814/http://www.fia.com/news/world-motor-sport-council-2014-beijing |archivedate=2015-08-07 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="15 calendar 2">{{cite news |title=World Motor Sport Council 2014 – Doha |work=FIA.com |publisher=[[Fédération_Internationale_de_l'Automobile|Fédération Internationale de l'Automobile]] |url=http://www.fia.com/node/9172 |date=2014-12-03 |accessdate=2015-03-01 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150319200239/http://www.fia.com/node/9172 |archivedate=2015-03-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>同時也是第85屆[[義大利大獎賽|義大利大獎賽]]。

在[[F1世界車手冠軍列表|車手冠軍積分榜]]上，[[梅賽德斯車隊|梅賽德斯]]車手[[路易斯·漢米爾頓|路易斯·漢米爾頓]]帶著領先隊友[[尼可·羅斯堡|尼可·羅斯堡]]28分的差距來到此站，緊追在後的是落後39分的[[法拉利車隊|法拉利]]車手[[賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾|賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾]]。梅賽德斯在[[一級方程式世界車隊冠軍列表|車隊冠軍積分榜]]上以184分的積分差距領先法拉利，位居第3的[[威廉斯車隊|威廉斯]]則以81分落後法拉利。

最終，漢米爾頓以領先亞軍得主維泰爾25秒之差，達成他職業生涯中的第2次[[大滿貫_(一級方程式賽車)|大滿貫]]及第40座分站冠軍，馬薩則取得季軍。羅斯堡在比賽最終3圈退賽，意味著漢米爾頓在積分榜上的領先地位擴大至53分。 幹事在賽後發現漢米爾頓的梅賽德斯其中一顆後輪胎壓低於倍耐力的建議最低標準，在經過幾個小時的調查後，漢米爾頓才得以穩坐此站的冠軍寶座。

== 賽事簡報 ==
=== 背景 ===
[[一級方程式輪胎|輪胎]]供應商[[倍耐力|倍耐力]]在此站將提供十支車隊四種輪胎配方。兩種乾胎選擇分別是作為「首選胎」的白色中性胎，以及作為「備選胎」的黃色軟胎，與該公司在[[2014年義大利大獎賽|前幾年]]提供作為首選胎的硬胎及備選胎的中性胎有所不同。<ref name="tyre"/>另外，雨胎有綠色半雨胎及藍色全雨胎兩款。[[薩伯車隊|薩伯車隊]]的賽道工程主管[[詹保羅·達爾阿拉|詹保羅·達爾阿拉]]（{{lang|it|Giampaolo Dall'Ara}}）讚揚這次全新的選擇，他認為這會增加車隊在彎道爭取時間及追求極速的挑戰性，將為車迷們帶來更精采的比賽。<ref name="tyre">{{cite web|url=http://www.gpupdate.net/en/f1-news/329607/pirelli-praised-for-sensible-monza-tyre-choice/|title=Monza tyre selection 'way more sensible'|work=GP Update|publisher=JHED Media BV|date=2015-08-31|accessdate=2015-09-01|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150907032554/http://www.gpupdate.net/en/f1-news/329607/pirelli-praised-for-sensible-monza-tyre-choice/|archivedate=2015-09-07|deadurl=no}}</ref>不過，在[[尼可·羅斯堡|尼可·羅斯堡]]及[[賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾|賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾]]於[[2015年比利時大獎賽|比利時大獎賽]]發生爆胎後，倍耐力仍收到來自一些車手及評論家的批評。<ref name=vettel2>{{cite web|title=F1: Sebastian Vettel attacks Pirelli after late tyre failure at Belgian Grand Prix|url=http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/aug/23/sebastian-vettel-attacks-pirelli-belgian-gp-failure|publisher=The Guardian|accessdate=2015-08-24|date=2015-08-23|language=en|archive-date=2015-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150824071302/http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/aug/23/sebastian-vettel-attacks-pirelli-belgian-gp-failure|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Coulthard|first1=David|title=David Coulthard column: Vettel right to tackle Pirelli on tyres|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/34043197|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2015-08-26|date=2015-08-24|language=en|archive-date=2015-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150825013028/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/34043197|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Hakkinen 'understands' Vettel's anger|url=http://www.planetf1.com/driver/55667788/74703/Hakkinen-understands-Vettels-anger|website=planetf1.com|accessdate=2015-08-29|date=2015-08-29|language=en|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150902074353/http://www.planetf1.com/driver/55667788/74703/Hakkinen-understands-Vettels-anger|archivedate=2015-09-02}}</ref>義大利大獎賽前，[[伯尼·埃克萊斯頓|伯尼·埃克萊斯頓]]呼籲這些車手關注好他們自己就好，表示：「我們還不打算讓他們（倍耐力）離開。他們現在做得正好。」<ref>{{cite web|last1=Weaver|first1=Paul|title=Bernie Ecclestone gags drivers from criticising F1 tyre manufacturers|url=http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/sep/04/bernie-ecclestone-wants-pirelli-to-remain-with-f1-beyond-2016|publisher=The Guardian|accessdate=2015-09-07|date=2015-09-04|language=en|archive-date=2015-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905221238/http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/sep/04/bernie-ecclestone-wants-pirelli-to-remain-with-f1-beyond-2016|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Benson|first1=Andrew|title=Italian GP: Drivers told to keep worries over Pirelli tyres private|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/34155703|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2015-09-07|date=2015-09-04|language=en|archive-date=2015-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150907090145/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/34155703|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[路特斯車隊|路特斯車隊]]的車輛在兩週前的比利時遭到當地法警扣押，他們已設法讓車輛趕回來參加大獎賽。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Johnson|first1=Daniel|title=Italian Grand Prix: Bailiffs release Lotus cars to make trip to Monza|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/motorsport/formulaone/11839904/Italian-Grand-Prix-Bailiffs-release-Lotus-cars-to-make-trip-to-Monza.html|publisher=The Telegraph|accessdate=2015-09-07|date=2015-09-02|language=en|archive-date=2015-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150907232117/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/motorsport/formulaone/11839904/Italian-Grand-Prix-Bailiffs-release-Lotus-cars-to-make-trip-to-Monza.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>儘管他們面臨著財務困難，但該隊依舊表示他們還有足夠的資金來參與剩餘的賽季。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Collantine|first1=Keith|title=Lotus 'has funds to complete the season'|url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/09/04/lotus-has-funds-to-complete-the-season/|publisher=F1Fanatic|accessdate=2015-09-07|date=2015-09-04|language=en|archive-date=2015-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150907012805/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/09/04/lotus-has-funds-to-complete-the-season/|dead-url=no}}</ref>另一方面，這次比賽週末前的其中一項熱門議題為合約談判，[[威廉斯車隊|威廉斯車隊]]宣布在{{F1|2016}}將留任[[費利佩·馬薩|費利佩·馬薩]]及[[維爾特利·鮑達斯|維爾特利·鮑達斯]]，<ref>{{cite web|title=Valtteri Bottas & Felipe Massa to remain at Williams in 2016|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/34138206|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2015-09-07|date=2015-09-03|language=en|archive-date=2015-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905211913/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/34138206|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Johnson|first1=Daniel|title=Hopes of return to Williams for Jenson Button dashed by new contract for Valtteri Bottas|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/motorsport/formulaone/11841160/Hopes-of-return-to-Williams-for-Jenson-Button-dashed-by-new-contract-for-Valtteri-Bottas.html|publisher=The Telegraph|accessdate=2015-09-07|date=2015-09-03|language=en|archive-date=2015-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906125649/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/motorsport/formulaone/11841160/Hopes-of-return-to-Williams-for-Jenson-Button-dashed-by-new-contract-for-Valtteri-Bottas.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>而[[尼克·胡肯伯格|尼克·胡肯伯格]]也與[[印度威力車隊|印度威力車隊]]簽下一份兩年合約。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Duncan|first1=Philip|title=Nico Hulkenberg signs new Force India contract to cap Le Mans success with two-year extension after missing out on Ferrari drive|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/motor-racing/nico-hulkenberg-signs-new-force-india-contract-to-cap-le-mans-success-with-twoyear-extension-after-missing-out-on-ferrari-drive-10481062.html|publisher=The Independent|accessdate=2015-09-07|date=2015-09-01|language=en|archive-date=2015-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905071055/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/motor-racing/nico-hulkenberg-signs-new-force-india-contract-to-cap-le-mans-success-with-twoyear-extension-after-missing-out-on-ferrari-drive-10481062.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>另外一個話題焦點即是蒙札的義大利大獎賽的未來性，其正面臨從賽曆中被刪除的風險。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Tremayne|first1=David|title=F1: Monza future in the balance as Bernie Ecclestone refuses to back down|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/motor-racing/f1-monza-future-in-the-balance-as-bernie-ecclestone-refuses-to-back-down-10488038.html|publisher=The Independent|accessdate=2015-09-07|date=2015-09-05|language=en|archive-date=2015-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150912022617/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/motor-racing/f1-monza-future-in-the-balance-as-bernie-ecclestone-refuses-to-back-down-10488038.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>義大利分站後，[[法拉利車隊|法拉利車隊]]的賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾提到他贊成繼續在這條賽道上舉辦大獎賽，說道：「如果我們因為一些低劣的金錢問題而把這場比賽從賽曆中剔除，基本上你已經在摧殘我們的內心了」。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Johnson|first1=Daniel|title=Italian Grand Prix 2015: Sebastian Vettel warns Bernie Ecclestone not to drop Monza from race calendar|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/motorsport/formulaone/11847935/Italian-Grand-Prix-2015-Sebastian-Vettel-warns-Bernie-Ecclestone-not-to-drop-Monza-from-race-calendar.html|publisher=The Telegraph|accessdate=2015-09-07|date=2015-09-06|language=en|archive-date=2015-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150907232137/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/motorsport/formulaone/11847935/Italian-Grand-Prix-2015-Sebastian-Vettel-warns-Bernie-Ecclestone-not-to-drop-Monza-from-race-calendar.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在技術開發方面，法拉利在主場用上他們的3次開發配額為引擎進行升級，[[梅賽德斯車隊|梅賽德斯]]則用完了他們的7次引擎配額。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/headlines/2015/9/mercedes-introduces-engine-upgrades-for-monza.html|title=Mercedes & Ferrari introduce engine upgrades for Monza|publisher=Formula One World Championship Limited|date=2015-09-04|website=Formula1.com|accessdate=2015-09-04|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150907034419/http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/headlines/2015/9/mercedes-introduces-engine-upgrades-for-monza.html|archivedate=2015-09-07|deadurl=no}}</ref>正因如此，梅賽德斯成為2015年賽季首支用完開發配額的車隊，[[本田車隊|本田]]及法拉利則還有4次配額，[[雷諾車隊|雷諾]]則剩12次留待剩餘賽季。
基於這些變更，兩輛梅賽德斯賽車皆換上他們本季的第3具動力單元，而兩輛法拉利則使用了第4具。另外，[[紅牛二隊|紅牛二隊]]、[[紅牛車隊|紅牛]]及[[麥拉倫車隊|麥拉倫]]皆因為超出使用零組件配額受到罰退，迫使他們將從發車格後段出發。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/headlines/2015/9/engine-penalties-loom-for-red-bull--mclaren--toro-rosso.html|title=Engine penalties loom for Red Bull, McLaren, Toro Rosso|publisher=Formula One World Championship Limited|date=2015-09-04|website=Formula1.com|accessdate=2015-09-04|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905053428/http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/headlines/2015/9/engine-penalties-loom-for-red-bull--mclaren--toro-rosso.html|archivedate=2015-09-05|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Verstappen also penalised for engine change|url=http://www.gpupdate.net/en/f1-news/329797/verstappen-also-penalised-for-engine-change/|work=gpupdate.net|publisher=gpupdate.net|date=2015-09-05|accessdate=2015-09-05|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150907035311/http://www.gpupdate.net/en/f1-news/329797/verstappen-also-penalised-for-engine-change/|archivedate=2015-09-07|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/headlines/2015/9/provisional-grid-for-italy-after-penalties.html|title=Provisional grid for Italy after penalties|publisher=Formula One World Championship Limited|date=2015-09-06|website=Formula1.com|accessdate=2015-09-06|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150907035407/http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/headlines/2015/9/provisional-grid-for-italy-after-penalties.html|archivedate=2015-09-07|deadurl=no}}</ref>

